name: Jan Read Artist
tag_list: pet-portraits, new-forest, landscapes, seascapes, figures, commissions, pastels
overview:
Pet portraits in pastels drawn to order from photographs.

Pet portrait commissions can be previewed online or via email before commiting to purchase.

Also available to purchase are Prints of Jan Read’s other works including, Landscapes, Seascapes, figures and other animals including a rather interesting Blue cow. Some originals are also available to Purchase.

Jan was originally a renowned local artist from Suffolk and has now moved to the New Forest where she is fast becoming established in the local art circles
